TableDefinition.DatabaseQuery: SELECT TOP 1 CASE (SmartCardPolicyOptions & 65536) WHEN '0' THEN 'False' ELSE 'True' END AS 'Allow unlock/logon on every computer', CASE (SmartCardPolicyOptions & 32768) WHEN '0' THEN 'False' ELSE 'True' END AS 'Use account password', CASE (SmartCardPolicyOptions & 16384) WHEN '0' THEN 'False' ELSE 'True' END AS 'Pincode complexity rules', CASE (SmartCardPolicyOptions & 8192) WHEN '0' THEN 'False' ELSE 'True' END AS 'Allow alphanumeriek values', CASE (SmartCardPolicyOptions & 4096) WHEN '0' THEN 'False' ELSE convert(varchar,PINExpiration) END AS 'Pincode expires in X days', CASE (SmartCardPolicyOptions & 1024) WHEN '0' THEN 'False' ELSE convert(varchar,PINMaxLength) END AS 'Pincode nolonger then X characters', CASE (SmartCardPolicyOptions & 512) WHEN '0' THEN 'False' ELSE convert(varchar,PINMinLength) END AS 'Pincode atleast X characters', CASE (SmartCardPolicyOptions & 256) WHEN '0' THEN 'False' ELSE 'True' END AS 'Allow unenrollment', CASE (SmartCardPolicyOptions & 128) WHEN '0' THEN 'False' ELSE 'True' END AS 'Allow multiple cards', CASE (SmartCardPolicyOptions & 64) WHEN '0' THEN 'False' ELSE convert(varchar,LogonWithoutPINInterval) END AS 'Allow cached login for X minutes', CASE (SmartCardPolicyOptions & 32) WHEN '0' THEN 'False' ELSE convert(varchar,UnlockWithoutPINInterval) END AS 'Allow cached unlock for X minutes', CASE (SmartCardPolicyOptions & 16) WHEN '0' THEN 'False' ELSE 'True' END AS 'Force smartcard login', CASE (SmartCardPolicyOptions & 8) WHEN '0' THEN 'False' ELSE 'True' END AS 'Force enrollement', CASE (SmartCardPolicyOptions & 4) WHEN '0' THEN 'False' ELSE 'True' END AS 'Ask for enrollement', CASE (SmartCardPolicyOptions & 1) WHEN '0' THEN 'False' ELSE 'True' END AS 'Disable Policy' FROM SmartCardPolicies WHERE IsDisabled = 0 ORDER BY SmartCardPolicyPreference DESC
